responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "E22618454B19D8785B1C969D04EB201E", "My brother, what great news! I look forward to the day Louie and I prevail against our enemies. We\'ll celebrate our triumphs in the name of our predecessors. But alas, today is not this day. Our progress demands everything from us. It\'s the cost of freedom on the frontier.")
